    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Blade &amp; Sorcery》是一款与众不同的中世纪奇幻游戏，专注于近战、远程与魔法战斗，并全面运用独特且真实的物理驱动交互与战斗系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作专为 VR 打造，碰撞精细计算，物体具有重量并遵循物理法则，生物拥有全身物理反馈与存在感，刀刃可以穿透软质材料或反弹魔法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/629730/extras/5cb31321452df3dd6b09b37f51b0885c.poster.avif?t=1765901841\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/629730/extras/5cb31321452df3dd6b09b37f51b0885c.webm?t=1765901841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/629730/extras/5cb31321452df3dd6b09b37f51b0885c.mp4?t=1765901841\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在“水晶狩猎”进程模式中展开冒险，解锁多达 78 种技能。探索地下城，深入拜斯的传说，揭开古代达尔加利安人的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在无限制的沙盒模式中畅玩，解锁全部 76 种武器和 90 件护甲，自由启用任意技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/629730/extras/bdf3f4a65a74439464c6dede7e85758d.poster.avif?t=1765901841\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/629730/extras/bdf3f4a65a74439464c6dede7e85758d.webm?t=1765901841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/629730/extras/bdf3f4a65a74439464c6dede7e85758d.mp4?t=1765901841\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Blade &amp; Sorcery》中，战斗的极限，只受你的创造力所限。选择你的武器，你的姿态，你的战斗风格；成为你梦寐以求的强大战士、游侠或法师吧！</p>",
